*klaptopdaemon-3.5.6-r1 (20 May 2007)

  20 May 2007; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org>
  +klaptopdaemon-3.5.6-r1.ebuild:
  Disable pointless binary checksum, bug #178554. Avoid unauthorised access
  when the system is supposed to be locked & hibernated, KDE bug #143859.

  18 May 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org>
  klaptopdaemon-3.5.5.ebuild, klaptopdaemon-3.5.6.ebuild:
  Disallow stripping because kcontrol complains about different size/checksum
  otherwise. Fixes bug 178554.

  29 Apr 2007; Carsten Lohrke <carlo@gentoo.org> klaptopdaemon-3.5.6.ebuild:
  Remove virtual/x11 dependency.

  05 Feb 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -files/kdeutils-3.4.3-klaptopdaemon.patch:
  Remove unneeded patches.

  04 Feb 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  -klaptopdaemon-3.5.2.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

